    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "debt-slaying? lol thats a weird way to put it. anyway, thanks for the formula. it just feels like some of these extra fees or ways they calculate interest are designed to keep the balance high. is there anything else i should watch out for that might eat into my payments?",
